            {
                type: 'text',
                title: 'social & environment responsibility',
                text: 'An advocate of sustainable design, Antonio is committed to designing quality environments making sustainable design an integral part of his design process. His core value is to design and create safe living environments, enhancing the health and well-being of people and communities. Antonio founded an on-profit organization, The Task Haiti Foundation and also owns and manages Advocate World wide an other non-profit organization. His sustainable design projects have won awards for many communities throughout the world.<br/><br/> Is it your dream to inspire people through international, world-class architecture, landscape and urban design? Whether you are a student or an experienced industry professional, D\'Antonio will stimulate and challenge your skills.'
